@mistercrayle actually ChingLiu's version did not have the MF error cracked, this was done by a user in audioz.info and is included in Mukundas' patch. But the best way currently is still using the original patches as described in audioz.info, because Mukundas added "funny" texts by a nut who called himself Anonymous, thus changing the actual program interface. The original audioz.info patched version runs perfectly, just no AAX plugins or MP3 bounce, but that is a small trade-off for an otherwise great program.
